section.contact-form.pinstripe
  .row
    h5 Contact Us
    h4 Send A Message To 
      span= practice.name
    p
      | If you have any questions, concerns, or comments regarding 
      span=practice.name  
      |, please fill out the short contact form below.
      
      form.contact_form
        .span6.left
          .label(property='form_name') Name
          input(name='form_name', type='text', value='', placeholder='Full name', required='true')
          .label(property='form_email') Email address
          input(name='form_email', type='email', value='', placeholder='Email address', required='true')
          .label(property='form_phone') Phone number
          input(name='form_phone', type='text', value='', placeholder='Phone number', required='')
        .span6.right
          .label(property='form_message') Comments
          textarea(name='form_message', cols='50', rows='10')
          input(type='checkbox' name='form_ack', required='true')
          label.ack_medical_condition(property='form_ack') I understand and agree that any information submitted will be forwarded to our office by email and not via a secure messaging system. This form should not be used to transmit private health information, and we disclaim all warranties with respect to the privacy and confidentiality of any information submitted through this form.
          br
          br
          //- button#js-contact-btn.btn-submit(type='submit') Send
          button.btn-submit(type='submit', value='Send', data-loading-msg='Submitting...', data-success-msg='Success!', data-error-msg='Error! Try again.') Send
